                    <span>a mix of cultures... musical styles.. not to say of alcohol, morphine,  etc... Jack fell sick on his trip to Mexico city, and he's looking for  healing, salvation- i believe he found it, with all the shots of morphine  he received at the hospital , with the mexican pulque and tequilla , and  other substances .. regardless it is a masterpiece of poetry. play some  "bird" in the background and enjoy!<p>"And I am only an  Apache -- Smoking Ashy -- In Old Cabashy -- By the Lamp!"</span>
                  
              
